SR NO. 130 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend Dr. E. Joseph Savoie on the occasion of his retirement for his
exemplary and selfless public service, visionary leadership, and extraordinary contributions
to higher education in Louisiana spanning nearly five decades; does hereby express profound
gratitude for his enduring commitment to the students, institutions, and residents of this
state; and does hereby extend sincere wishes for continued happiness, health, and success
in all of his future endeavors.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Dr.
E. Joseph Savoie.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
